title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in a group row.
EB: The export process should successfully export data from tables that contain highlight or map features without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Add a table with a group row and include a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report.
3. Attempt to export the data.
